# iOS & iPadOS Release Notes

Learn about changes to the iOS & iPadOS SDK.

## Overview

Release notes provide details on API changes, known issues, fixes, workarounds, and deprecations for recent software releases.

### Bug Reporting

For issues not mentioned in release notes, send feedback through [applefeedback://].

When writing your report, please include the full version number in the title and in the description. This looks like “13 (17A_xxxx_).” You can find the full version number in Settings > General > About > Version. For more information, visit [https://developer.apple.com/bug-reporting/].
